ua.chernov.taskmanager.transport

Interface Packets


  • public interface Packets
    Transport packets, sent using serialization. Protocol: #handshake: Client -> Server: Register(username) Server -> Client: Ok | RuntimeException #main loop: Client -> Server: Message(user,body) Server -> Client: Message(user,body) | Join(user) | Part(user) #end: Client -> Server: Part Serve -> Client: Ok | RuntimeException
